\v 1 Impukane ezifileyo zinukisa zibilise\x + Hlab. 145.7.\x* amagcobo omthaki\x + Eks. 30.25.\x*; ubuthutha obuncinyane \add benza njalo k\add*ohloniphekayo ngenxa yenhlakanipho \add lo\add*dumo\x + 2.3.\x*.
\v 2 Inhliziyo yohlakaniphileyo ingakwesokunene sakhe, kodwa inhliziyo yesithutha ingakwesokhohlo saso.
\v 3 Yebo-ke lapho oyisithutha ehamba endleleni, ingqondo yakhe iyasilela, uthi kuye wonke uyisithutha\x + Zaga 18.2.\x*.
