\v 4 Uba umoya wombusi ukuvukela, ungatshiyi indawo yakho\x + 8.3.\x*, ngoba ukuthobeka\x + Zaga 14.30. 15.4. Jer. 8.15. Zaga 4.22.\x* kuyathulisa iziphambeko ezinkulu\x + Zaga 25.15.\x*.
\v 5 Kulobubi \add e\add*ngibubone ngaphansi kwelanga, njengesiphosiso esiphuma ebusweni\x + 5.6.\x* bombusi\x + 7.19.\x*:
\v 6 Ubuwula bubekwa ezindaweni eziphakemeyo kakhulu, labanothileyo bahlala endaweni ephansi\x + Zaga 28.12. 29.2.\x*.
\v 7 Ngibonile izigqili\x + Zaga 19.10.\x* zigade amabhiza, leziphathamandla zihamba njengezigqili emhlabeni\x + Esta 6.8. Jer. 17.25. Hez. 23.12.\x*.
