\v 8 Ogebha umgodi uzawela kuwo\x + Hlab. 7.15.\x*; lodiliza umthangala\x + Isa. 5.5.\x*, inyoka izamluma\x + Amos 5.19.\x*.
\v 9 Osusa amatshe uzalinyazwa yiwo\x + Dute. 27.17. 2 Kho. 3.25.\x*; obanda izigodo uzakuba sengozini ngazo\x + Dute. 20.19.\x*.
\v 10 Uba insimbi ibuthundu\x + Jer. 31.29,30. Hez. 18.2.\x* njalo engaloli ubukhali\x + Hez. 21.21.\x*, ngakho ufanele engezelele amandla; kodwa inhlakanipho yinhle\x + 1.3.\x* ukulungisa\x + 11.6.\x*.
