\v 11 Uba inyoka iluma kungelakulunjwa\x + Isa. 3.3. 26.16. Jer. 8.17. Hlab. 58.5.\x*, kakulanzuzo kungcitshi yolimi\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 12 Amazwi omlomo ohlakaniphileyo alomusa\x + Zaga 10.32.\x*, kodwa indebe zesithutha ziyasiginya\x + Zaga 18.7.\x*.
\v 13 Ukuqala kwamazwi omlomo waso kuyibuthutha\x + 2.3.\x*, lokucina kwenkulumo yaso kuyibuhlanya obubi\x + 1.17.\x*,
\v 14 njalo isithutha sandisa amazwi\x + Zaga 15.2.\x*. Umuntu kazi okuzakuba khona; lalokho okuzakuba khona emva kwakhe\x + 3.22.\x*, ngubani ongamtshela khona\x + 8.7.\x*?
\v 15 Umtshikatshika wesithuthandini uyasidinisa, ngoba kasazi ukuya emzini.
