\v 16 Maye kuwe, lizwe\x + 4.10.\x*, onkosi\x + Isa. 3.4,5,12.\x* yakho ingumntwana\x + 2 Lan. 13.7.\x*, leziphathamandla zakho zidla ekuseni\x + Isa. 5.11.\x*!
\v 17 Ubusisiwe, lizwe, onkosi yakho iyindodana yabakhulu, leziphathamandla zakho zidla ngesikhathi esifaneleyo, \add zidl\add*ela ukuqina, hatshi ukudakwa\x + Zaga 31.4.\x*.
